 have Employee Dishonesty Bonds when one or more employees handle cash or company assets.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][qode_elements_holder number_of_columns="two_columns"][qode_elements_holder_item background_color="#cccccc"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\nI am text block. Click edit button to change this text. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis, pulvinar dapibus leo.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/qode_elements_holder_item][/qode_elements_holder][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Bond Insurance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16066-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-12 14:14:56', '2016-04-12 14:14:56', '', 16066, 'http://blissmarc.com/16066-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(16107, 1, '2016-05-27 16:31:16', '2016-05-27 16:31:16', '[vc_row type="grid" background_image="16114"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="100px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_separator color="#999999"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\n<h1>Health &amp; Life Insurance</h1>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Bliss Marc works with some of the largest companies to help provide you and your employees with the best Health and Life Insurance options. We will work with you directly to create a health insurance plan that will meet the ever-changing needs of both you and your employees. There is never a company too small to cover and we will ensure you have a provider that works with a large network of hospitals, doctors and specialists.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Health Insurance</strong></span>\n\n&nbsp;\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="http://blissmarc.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/blissmarcindividualhealthinsurance.pdf" target="_blank">Individual Health Insurance Coverage Application</a> (PDF)</li>\n	<li><a href="http://blissmarc.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/blissmarcgrouphealthinsurance.pdf" target="_blank">Group Health Insurance Coverage Application</a> (PDF)</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n\nDomestic only, for example, Bliss Marc proudly provides Blue Shield of California. Begin the <strong><a href="https://www.blueshieldca.com/bsc/ApplyNow?xyz=IOY48Zi8o2%2Fo" target="_blank">quotation process</a> </strong>immediately!\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>Proud provider: </em></strong><a href="http://blissmarc.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/800px-Blue_Shield_of_California.svg_.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-16260" src="http://blissmarc.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/800px-Blue_Shield_of_California.svg_-300x79.png" alt="800px-Blue_Shield_of_California.svg" width="300" height="79" /></a></p>\n\n&nbsp;\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Globally, Bliss Marc can provide coverage for all your expatriate health needs. The benefits of our international health insurance include: access to several thousand worldwide medical centers, physicians, and nursing staff in more than 160 countries. In addition, we can arrange emergency transport to the nearest appropriate medical center, or repatriation. Click <strong>Here</strong> to learn more.</p>\n\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_separator color="#999999"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Life Insurance</strong></span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAn investment in you and your family’s future! Life covers your families, or beneficiary of choice in case of death in the form funds to pay bills, loss of income, or any other potential expenses. We offer Term Life insurance to pay the beneficiary a sum of money in the unlikely event of death within a term, such as 5, 10, 15, 20 or 30 years. We also offer Whole or Permanent Life insurance has a higher monthly payment, but that has a "cash value," and can be accessed in the form of a loan. Click <strong>Here</strong> for more information.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Health / Life Insurance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16064-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-05-27 16:31:16', '2016-05-27 16:31:16', '', 16064, 'http://blissmarc.com/16064-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
