(15985, 1, '2015-08-13 14:20:29', '2015-08-13 14:20:29', '[vc_row row_type="parallax" use_row_as_full_screen_section="yes" type="full_width" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" side_padding="0" background_image="15975"][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_empty_space height="100px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>Bliss Marc University</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_separator type="normal" position="center" color="#f7f7f7" width_in_percentages=""][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]Welcome to Bliss Marc University! Bliss Marc University has established a robust, top notch online training system to help healthcare organizations and professionals with continued education, development and training needs. Our main focus is primarily home health care and hospice organizations, but our courses span across all types of healthcare. We offer 100% accredited courses certified by ASRT, ARRT, ANCC, NAB and OSHA. Our course catalog provides a wide selection of classes for skilled nurses, nurses’ assistants, physical therapists and assistants, home health care aides and healthcare administration.\r\n\r\nIn working with many healthcare professionals and organizations, Bliss Marc identified the problems many agencies face regarding training. Companies find it difficult to get their employees in the same place and at the same time for training.\r\n\r\nThey were also spending additional money to bring in an outside professional to lead the training courses.\r\n\r\nWith the ever changing healthcare environment, home health care agencies were concerned with having consistent, relevant and up to date training information. This is where Bliss Marc University can help you. With over 200 courses available, Bliss Marc University makes it easy to to fulfill state and federal license renewal requirements.\r\n\r\nFor more information or to log in to the course catalog, <a href="#">click here</a>.\r\n\r\nBliss Marc serves clients nationwide and works with some of the largest insurance companies in the United States.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Workers Compensation', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '15671-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-08-13 14:20:29', '2015-08-13 14:20:29', '', 15671, 'http://blissmarc.com/15671-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
