(16310, 1, '2016-05-28 13:35:52', '2016-05-28 13:35:52', '[vc_row type="grid" background_image="16149"][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="100px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h1>Background Checks</h1>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_separator color="#999999"][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Employee Screenings</strong></span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Ensuring the safety of patients is critical to healthcare organizations.  We understand your need to investigate a prospective employee especially if that employee will have access to confidential information, administering medications and responsible for caregiving to your clients.  Verifying an employee’s background is critical to minimizing risks to your patients and to your organization.  Comply with the Health Care Worker Background Check Act through Bliss Marc.</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]Our background check services can be purchased individually or in package form. Below are some of the reports available:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Medical License Verification</li>\r\n 	<li>Motor Vehicle Report</li>\r\n 	<li>National and State Criminal Report</li>\r\n 	<li>Employment History</li>\r\n 	<li>Credit Reports</li>\r\n 	<li>Professional License</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Screening Vendors &amp; Companies</strong></span></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]Partnering with a new company is a big decision with economic consequences and culpability.  The last thing that you want to worry about is the reputation and credit worthiness of your new partner. Bliss Marc can help screen for your background checks and you will no longer have concerns about what you don’t know about your new business alliances.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][vc_column_text]Bliss Marc will do background checks that confirm the new business partner’s contact information, assets, business licenses, and all corporate filings. In addition, we check credit, public, and court records for potential bill payment, tax, or litigation issues. We then provide an assessment of the information that we have gathered so that you have an at-a-glance summary of the new partner that you are evaluating. Whether you are a small business looking to expand or an established business with new partners seeking you out, we can help you fully verify your potential business partners in order to dramatically minimize your risk.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="20px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"]\r\n[/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height="50px"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Background Checks', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '16074-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-28 13:35:52', '2016-05-28 13:35:52', '', 16074, 'http://blissmarc.com/16074-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
